page.title: 11 JANES TYPICAL DAY.
page.content:
My day starts by getting up at 7.30 a.m. Mum would get up and make breakfast.I have my breakfast then get dressed and washed.Then I walk to the crossroads to catch the bus at 8.05.
At school we wait outside in the playground.Then a teacher comes out and we line up and go in.At 9.00 we have assembly until 9.30.Then we do maths (triangles) until its time for play.After, we write a story.Next it is lunch .After that we have play and then we had games until 2.15. After break our teacher reads to us until 3.00.Then I get on the bus and go home. At home I watch TV until tea. After tea I go out to play on my bike or with my friends until its time to go to bed.
